    "Name": "Dengier DG1-OA",
    "Details": "The DG1-OA configuration pairs a Hatchet with a Small Shield opposite, giving it a distinctly aggressive close-quarters identity. An Apollo FCS-guided MRM 30 delivers heavy missile salvos while an ER PPC and twin ER Medium Lasers handle direct fire at range. The shield trades some offensive output for meaningful defensive resilience, making this loadout notably harder to put down in the close-range engagements it actively seeks.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Protected Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
